                <h1>Discover Hawaii's Capital: Honolulu</h1>
                <p>The capital of Hawaii is Honolulu, located on the island of Oahu. Known for its stunning beaches, vibrant culture, and rich history, Honolulu serves as the primary gateway to the Hawaiian Islands. The city is famous for landmarks such as Waikiki Beach, Pearl Harbor, and Diamond Head, offering a unique blend of urban and natural beauty.</p>
